Title: Living in the world of the unknown.
DateModified: '2019-02-17'
DatePublished: '2019-02-17'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/living-in-the-world-of-the-unknown
SetInCountry: Greece
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Tiffi Satterfield
AuthorCountry: United States of America
Text: We have millions of opportunities but only one life. What we do in this time,
  is vital for humanity and generations to come.  I devote my life to human kindness.
  Fascinating on my theory,  of adaptability, and love for all . Have you wondered
  what it would be like, if traveling was free and you could visit any place in the
  world? Where would you go, what would you do, who would you see,  what would you
  want to experience, and most importantly what did you learn?  My mission in life,
  is  traveling the world, adapting to every culture,  Learning life from others point
  of view, seeking to understand, and ultimately  manifesting love to everyone. We
  live in this world full of unknown, if we could catch a glimpse of Agape love, life
  would be everlasting.
